Task 1 – Description (Brief)

In this task, I created a digital literacy awareness infographic to help students understand the importance of digital skills in today’s world. I used Canva to design a visually engaging poster that explains what digital literacy means and why it is essential for students.

The infographic includes key topics such as smart online tools, safe internet practices, professional online presence, and email etiquette. I focused on presenting the information in a simple, clear, and attractive way so that it is easy for students to understand at a glance.

This task helped me learn how to communicate important information visually and effectively. It also improved my design skills and gave me a better understanding of how digital literacy impacts academic and professional success.
